songs.title: To Be Fine
songs.lyrics:
Why are there lighters in me?
Do you do that for me?

I know you want to run
It will not only be fun
You just have to take the Gun

Just for me
Do you do this just for me?
It is in me, it is in you
This is to be good
I just want to be good
Just be fine
I do not want to be on the line
End my life
